    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_1_1_05f48829["1.1 This standard specifies the<br/>requirements for achieving, assuring and<br/>managing the safety of PSS defined by<br/>the scope of contract."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_1_2_e5039df5["1.2 The contractor, together with the UK<br/>MOD, has responsibility for safety of<br/>all deliverable PSS."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_1_3_5f521dcf["1.3 The responsibility of the contractor<br/>also varies with the scope of analysis."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_1_4_49eac461["1.4 Whilst contract life might be<br/>limited, this standard considers the<br/>whole life cycle of the PSS, including<br/>disposal."]
